About the author:

Spencer Krum lives and works in Minneapolis. He has been on the command line since he was 12 and has been flinging root shells professionally for seven years.

Inspiration:

The cast draws on the techniques of the Day[9] Daily, with content inspired by the CAT's Braindump.
